t("The black flame around #Target# dies down", "#Target#周围的邪恶火焰熄灭了", "_t")
t("-Fiery Torment", "-灼魂之罚", "_t")
t("fire", "火焰", "effect subtype")
t("Destroyer", "毁灭者", "_t")
t("The target assumes the form of a powerful demon.", "目标变形为强大的恶魔。", "tformat")
